{"tid":2361858,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★支化產品】異常天氣令 Apple Watch讀數出錯  無法得知何時可解決！","createTime":"2021-01-11T04:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T06:48:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb87a870041e797d447bda66cecba1e2a85f45d","tid":2361858,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"近期德國的大量 Apple Watch 用戶反應稱，自己的手錶在近期海拔高度讀數誤差很大。絕大部分用戶表示，此前使用過程正常，但是近期其高度計信息顯示海拔高度被算高了200至300米。<br />\n<br />\n從 Apple 德國支援論壇上的信息可以發現，導致近期手錶高度計顯示異常的原因在於異常的低氣壓天氣。低氣壓導致高度計讀數偏高，讓讀數與現實不符合。<br />\n<br />\n通常氣壓異常導致高度計異常的情況是很常見的，這個時候只需要重新進行校準就可以解決問題。但這對於 Apple 的產品來說，就是一個大問題。首先是 Apple 不允許用戶手動進行高度計重新校準，第二是不知道 Apple Watch 自動重新校準的時間間隔，無法得知什麼時候問題才能得到解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2021/01/10/suddenly-abnormal-weather-makes-apple-watch-altimeter-error/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2021%2F01%2F10%2Fsuddenly-abnormal-weather-makes-apple-watch-altimeter-error%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7TFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=ac5407e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2021/01/10/suddenly-abnormal-weather-makes-apple-watch-altimeter-error/</a>"},{"pid":"ccc033ff11d3d77d54fb44dbd2e4697ae1e5824b","tid":2361858,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"Gay cook:用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關人"},{"pid":"7fa862ae3e312e8a02f60c700f96d6d9e34eba72","tid":2361858,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:54:55.000Z","msg":"衰過淘寶貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec7b3bbbdaa9403e2b8df41946b903f765fbb8a","tid":2361858,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":